desc: Dipt is next generation nail technology. A professional soak off system using premium grade resins and a finely milled acrylic powder. Designed and manufactured in the UK using the best of British Chemistry. Dipt changes the way you apply and wear semi-permanent colour as an alternative to gel polish.

layout.text: A pop of pinky coral to boost your day ! The kit includes 1oz Spirit powder, all 4 liquids and a Flamingo file.
